WEBVTT

00:01:35.890 --> 00:01:38.190
[Too Young To Love]

00:01:38.570 --> 00:01:41.140
[Episode 24]

00:01:41.640 --> 00:01:43.039
Ever since Lan came back,

00:01:43.320 --> 00:01:45.250
I can see you have a lot on your mind.

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:47.560
I'm fine.

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:48.850
Just a few things

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:50.330
going on at work lately.

00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:53.080
I'm not

00:01:53.430 --> 00:01:54.759
the most observant man.

00:01:57.009 --> 00:01:57.670
Be careful.

00:01:59.000 --> 00:01:59.720
But your mom

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:01.300
did tell me that...

00:02:02.220 --> 00:02:03.650
things aren't right

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:05.130
between you and Lan.

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:08.570
Why didn't Mom

00:02:08.910 --> 00:02:10.280
ask me herself?

00:02:11.710 --> 00:02:12.780
Your mom

00:02:12.810 --> 00:02:14.830
always goes along with whatever you want.

00:02:14.830 --> 00:02:16.800
If there's something
you don't want to talk about,

00:02:16.800 --> 00:02:18.260
she naturally won't push.

00:02:19.560 --> 00:02:21.120
But I feel that you've been

00:02:21.380 --> 00:02:22.780
more and more off lately.

00:02:23.310 --> 00:02:24.360
Do you need me

00:02:24.380 --> 00:02:25.380
to help you fix it?

00:02:25.600 --> 00:02:26.440
Dad,

00:02:26.710 --> 00:02:27.870
I'm a grown man now.

00:02:28.500 --> 00:02:29.760
I can handle it myself.

00:02:31.640 --> 00:02:33.210
I'll say what I always say.

00:02:34.390 --> 00:02:35.970
Whatever decision you make,

00:02:35.970 --> 00:02:36.890
I support you.

00:02:38.470 --> 00:02:39.430
You don't need to

00:02:39.450 --> 00:02:40.980
worry about your mom and me.

00:02:40.980 --> 00:02:42.640
We can take care of ourselves.

00:02:43.650 --> 00:02:44.530
A man

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:46.970
should build a family and a career.

00:02:47.570 --> 00:02:49.230
You need to have your own life—

00:02:49.630 --> 00:02:51.420
a wife and children.

00:02:52.590 --> 00:02:53.280
Dad,

00:02:54.310 --> 00:02:55.940
I've only been gone a short while.

00:02:55.940 --> 00:02:58.000
Why are you suddenly nagging so much?

00:03:01.150 --> 00:03:02.750
If you decide to get married,

00:03:02.910 --> 00:03:04.030
I'll prepare the marital home

00:03:04.030 --> 00:03:05.620
and the betrothal gifts for you.

00:03:05.620 --> 00:03:07.350
We can't let her feel slighted.

00:03:07.450 --> 00:03:10.580
She should marry into our family
with dignity and style.

00:03:11.970 --> 00:03:12.540
I know.

00:03:13.620 --> 00:03:14.680
You little rascal.

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:48.000
-Auntie.
-Lan, you're here.

00:03:49.610 --> 00:03:50.700
Here to see Xiaole?

00:03:52.600 --> 00:03:54.640
Xiaole will be back soon.
Wait for him a bit.

00:03:54.640 --> 00:03:55.310
Okay.

00:03:56.240 --> 00:03:57.470
Are you cleaning?

00:03:57.490 --> 00:03:58.230
Need a hand?

00:03:59.590 --> 00:04:01.920
There are some big boxes in Xiaole's room.

00:04:01.950 --> 00:04:03.340
Why don't you help me sort through them?

00:04:03.340 --> 00:04:04.080
Okay, sure.

00:04:39.130 --> 00:04:40.980
[May you have much joy and peace.]

00:04:40.980 --> 00:04:44.750
♪ Some remain forever young and free ♪

00:04:44.970 --> 00:04:49.070
♪ In their eyes, I see you and me ♪

00:04:49.150 --> 00:04:53.210
♪ The lonely air surrounds me ♪

00:04:53.770 --> 00:04:59.820
♪ Shutting out the noise
and all the warmth ♪

00:05:00.840 --> 00:05:04.730
♪ I wish I could be a goldfish ♪

00:05:04.820 --> 00:05:08.690
♪ With its so-called seven-second memory ♪

00:05:08.940 --> 00:05:11.000
♪ Seven was the moment we first met,
and six was when we grew close ♪

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.870
I got into Hailan University!

00:05:13.060 --> 00:05:15.730
♪ Now, there's just an empty space
beside me where you should be ♪

00:05:15.730 --> 00:05:17.210
Hello, schoolmate.

00:05:17.450 --> 00:05:17.500
Hello, schoolmate.

00:05:17.500 --> 00:05:21.220
♪ Just let me become a goldfish ♪

00:05:21.510 --> 00:05:24.200
♪ So I wouldn't be swallowed
by memories anymore ♪

00:05:24.200 --> 00:05:25.200
[Sha Baitian's
Photography Solo Exhibition]

00:05:25.520 --> 00:05:28.490
♪ Five was all the hugs we shared,
and four was the moment we broke up ♪

00:05:28.490 --> 00:05:29.650
[The sky I shot on the plane
after you broke up with me.]

00:05:29.650 --> 00:05:30.470
♪ Three, two, one, and I can finally ♪

00:05:30.470 --> 00:05:32.100
[Can't sleep. I'm thinking of you.]

00:05:32.130 --> 00:05:34.130
[I wish you happiness.]

00:05:34.159 --> 00:05:34.490
[Trees bloom and seas stretch far.]

00:05:34.490 --> 00:05:37.420
♪ Forget you ♪

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:41.960
[Trees bloom and seas stretch far.]
[I wish you happiness.]

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:43.810
[The sky I shot on the plane
after you broke up with me.]

00:05:43.840 --> 00:05:45.780
[Can't sleep. I'm thinking of you.]

00:05:48.960 --> 00:05:50.510
[At New Year's, I bought sparklers
and made a wish for you.]

00:05:50.510 --> 00:05:54.400
♪ I wish I could be a goldfish ♪

00:05:54.500 --> 00:05:54.710
♪ With its so-called seven-second memory ♪

00:05:54.710 --> 00:05:58.620
[I whispered that I miss you.]

00:05:58.620 --> 00:06:02.480
♪ Seven was the moment we first met,
and six was when we grew close ♪

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:06.850
♪ Now, there's just an empty space
beside me where you should be ♪

00:06:07.170 --> 00:06:08.130
♪ Just let me become a goldfish ♪

00:06:08.130 --> 00:06:11.180
[Tong Xiaole; Flight Ticket]

00:06:11.180 --> 00:06:14.940
♪ So I wouldn't be swallowed
by memories anymore ♪

00:06:15.190 --> 00:06:15.790
♪ Five was all the hugs we shared,
and four was the moment we broke up ♪

00:06:15.790 --> 00:06:18.350
[Tong Xiaole; Flight Ticket]

00:06:19.320 --> 00:06:23.600
♪ Three, two, one, and I can finally ♪

00:06:24.160 --> 00:06:27.090
♪ Forget you ♪

00:06:50.070 --> 00:06:51.000
Be careful, Dad.

00:06:52.510 --> 00:06:53.240
You're back.

00:07:00.600 --> 00:07:01.040
Mom.

00:07:01.690 --> 00:07:02.420
Where is Lan?

00:07:03.180 --> 00:07:03.910
She was here,

00:07:04.040 --> 00:07:05.040
but she went back.

00:07:06.520 --> 00:07:09.320
Oh, right, Lan left something for you
in your room.

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:10.930
Okay.

00:07:10.940 --> 00:07:12.470
I'll... I'll go take a look.

00:07:50.270 --> 00:07:50.950
Yi Lan!

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:00.700
What do you mean?

00:08:02.380 --> 00:08:03.580
What do you mean?

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:06.220
That question mark—what does it mean?

00:08:07.630 --> 00:08:08.690
You came to find me,

00:08:08.890 --> 00:08:11.420
but didn't come to see me.
What does that mean?

00:08:12.710 --> 00:08:13.670
Then tell me,

00:08:14.390 --> 00:08:15.920
why did you break up with me?

00:08:16.120 --> 00:08:17.210
I asked you first!

00:08:17.270 --> 00:08:18.730
You broke up with me first.

00:08:22.960 --> 00:08:23.760
Because...

00:08:27.250 --> 00:08:28.770
after we got together,

00:08:28.900 --> 00:08:30.700
you were all I could think about.

00:08:31.260 --> 00:08:33.059
I wanted to be with you every day!

00:08:33.470 --> 00:08:34.870
I didn't want that kind of life!

00:08:34.870 --> 00:08:37.669
I didn't want my entire life
to revolve around you!

00:08:37.919 --> 00:08:38.720
I wanted...

00:08:40.250 --> 00:08:41.909
I wanted to find myself again.

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:48.630
I'm done.

00:08:49.170 --> 00:08:49.770
Your turn.

00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:05.810
I admit it.

00:09:07.630 --> 00:09:08.960
I did go looking for you.

00:09:10.270 --> 00:09:11.170
I watched you from a distance,

00:09:11.170 --> 00:09:12.320
and you looked so free,

00:09:12.320 --> 00:09:13.250
so at ease.

00:09:13.280 --> 00:09:14.340
Just like you said,

00:09:14.890 --> 00:09:16.220
you had found yourself.

00:09:16.350 --> 00:09:18.780
I was also afraid that
if I'd suddenly shown up in front of you,

00:09:18.780 --> 00:09:20.250
I'd mess up your rhythm again

00:09:20.250 --> 00:09:22.100
and make you lose yourself again!

00:09:22.100 --> 00:09:22.980
You never even asked me.

00:09:22.980 --> 00:09:24.990
How would you know if I was doing well?

00:09:24.990 --> 00:09:26.430
How would you know if I was truly happy

00:09:26.430 --> 00:09:27.460
or just pretending?

00:09:27.460 --> 00:09:27.980
Yeah!

00:09:28.430 --> 00:09:29.240
I came!

00:09:29.260 --> 00:09:30.060
But then what?

00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:32.610
You were surrounded by a crowd of men!

00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:33.980
Did I even matter?

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:34.720
Suppose I'd told you

00:09:34.720 --> 00:09:35.320
at the time,

00:09:35.320 --> 00:09:36.320
"Yi Lan, I still like you.

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:37.140
I still care about you.

00:09:37.140 --> 00:09:38.630
I still want to be with you!"

00:09:38.630 --> 00:09:39.960
And what if you'd replied, "Tong Xiaole,

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:41.320
I don't have feelings for you anymore"?

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:42.520
What should I do then?

00:09:44.310 --> 00:09:48.270
♪ I still can't forget the tenderness
you gave me that year ♪

00:09:48.350 --> 00:09:51.990
♪ Exhausting all my strength,
I still can't fool myself ♪

00:09:52.200 --> 00:09:52.380
Mom.

00:09:52.380 --> 00:09:53.360
♪ Your place is still here ♪

00:09:53.360 --> 00:09:53.910
Look.

00:09:54.720 --> 00:09:55.140
Don't look.

00:09:55.140 --> 00:09:55.690
Go, go.

00:09:55.690 --> 00:09:59.470
♪ No one else can take it ♪

00:10:00.290 --> 00:10:00.780
♪ Let me treat it as just a heavy rain ♪

00:10:00.780 --> 00:10:01.840
How does that feel?

00:10:04.050 --> 00:10:06.260
♪ Gradually, the memories we've built
become clear ♪

00:10:06.260 --> 00:10:06.950
Yi Lan!

00:10:07.560 --> 00:10:08.850
We're just friends now!

00:10:08.850 --> 00:10:08.860
♪ All composed into a song ♪

00:10:08.860 --> 00:10:10.210
What right do you have to kiss me?

00:10:10.210 --> 00:10:12.540
Answer me—how do you feel about that kiss?

00:10:13.670 --> 00:10:14.640
♪ Hidden deep inside my heart ♪

00:10:14.640 --> 00:10:15.700
Then let me ask you—

00:10:16.100 --> 00:10:17.290
what are we now?

00:10:19.250 --> 00:10:21.250
I'll give you one chance. You say it.

00:10:26.550 --> 00:10:27.970
I'll give you a chance.

00:10:28.960 --> 00:10:30.060
What are we?

00:10:33.640 --> 00:10:34.740
I'm not saying it!

00:10:47.910 --> 00:10:48.370
Sister!

00:10:52.020 --> 00:10:55.060
Were you kissing Xiaole
in the park just now?

00:10:55.090 --> 00:10:55.950
That wasn't me.

00:10:57.390 --> 00:10:59.790
That wasn't me!
How could it possibly be me?

00:11:05.840 --> 00:11:06.770
If it wasn't you,

00:11:07.440 --> 00:11:08.500
could it be that...

00:11:08.880 --> 00:11:10.350
Xiaole cheated?

00:11:12.830 --> 00:11:14.140
That's outrageous.

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:16.500
First of all,

00:11:16.500 --> 00:11:19.170
we warmly welcome you all
to celebrate the New Year with us.

00:11:19.170 --> 00:11:20.680
May we all be happy

00:11:20.710 --> 00:11:21.770
and healthy.

00:11:21.870 --> 00:11:22.620
And may you two,

00:11:22.620 --> 00:11:23.710
the future couple,

00:11:24.420 --> 00:11:25.770
be full of happiness.

00:11:26.080 --> 00:11:27.740
And I also wish that my son here

00:11:28.210 --> 00:11:29.750
will successfully
get into college next year.

00:11:29.750 --> 00:11:30.270
Okay?

00:11:30.290 --> 00:11:31.650
-Come on!
-Cheers!

00:11:31.780 --> 00:11:32.320
Bottoms up!

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:33.000
Cheers!

00:11:33.430 --> 00:11:34.580
Happy New Year.

00:11:34.630 --> 00:11:35.360
Come on.

00:11:37.310 --> 00:11:38.310
Slow down.

00:11:39.010 --> 00:11:40.210
It's fine. Let's eat.

00:11:40.260 --> 00:11:40.930
Let's dig in.

00:11:40.930 --> 00:11:41.450
Come on.

00:11:41.470 --> 00:11:42.440
Help yourself.

00:11:42.710 --> 00:11:43.640
Here, daughter.

00:11:44.720 --> 00:11:45.200
Okay.

00:11:45.230 --> 00:11:45.660
Dad.

00:11:45.800 --> 00:11:46.470
Here.

00:11:46.600 --> 00:11:47.660
Thank you, Xiaole.

00:11:48.290 --> 00:11:49.130
Tong.

00:11:50.000 --> 00:11:50.600
We've

00:11:50.830 --> 00:11:51.710
been thinking—

00:11:52.240 --> 00:11:53.300
after the New Year,

00:11:53.650 --> 00:11:54.910
maybe we could arrange

00:11:55.200 --> 00:11:56.960
an engagement party for them or something.

00:11:56.960 --> 00:11:57.420
No need!

00:11:57.780 --> 00:11:58.250
Dad,

00:11:58.510 --> 00:11:59.340
there's no rush.

00:11:59.340 --> 00:12:00.810
We have our own plans.

00:12:01.960 --> 00:12:02.440
Dad.

00:12:05.270 --> 00:12:05.790
Uncle.

00:12:06.480 --> 00:12:08.000
My photography work

00:12:08.020 --> 00:12:09.550
has been quite busy lately.

00:12:09.790 --> 00:12:11.420
There's really no hurry.

00:12:11.630 --> 00:12:13.370
I've got the betrothal gifts ready.

00:12:13.370 --> 00:12:14.200
I've bought them

00:12:14.200 --> 00:12:15.530
an apartment downtown.

00:12:16.110 --> 00:12:18.120
We'll handle
the engagement party together,

00:12:18.120 --> 00:12:19.630
and you two just need to show up.

00:12:19.630 --> 00:12:21.030
Young people nowadays

00:12:21.050 --> 00:12:22.970
don't like
all these complicated formalities.

00:12:22.970 --> 00:12:23.770
That's right.

00:12:23.830 --> 00:12:24.200
Yes.

00:12:24.760 --> 00:12:25.240
Right?

00:12:25.270 --> 00:12:25.670
Yes.

00:12:26.020 --> 00:12:26.940
Let's eat.

00:12:27.000 --> 00:12:27.460
Come on.

00:12:28.820 --> 00:12:29.750
Come on, cheers.

00:12:29.870 --> 00:12:31.190
H-Have a drink with him.

00:12:31.190 --> 00:12:31.670
Cheers.

00:12:31.720 --> 00:12:32.810
-Cheers.
-Come on.

00:12:34.630 --> 00:12:35.320
Yes.

00:12:36.650 --> 00:12:38.340
I-In my life,

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:40.920
I'm only marrying off my daughter once.

00:12:41.200 --> 00:12:41.830
Dad.

00:12:43.170 --> 00:12:44.090
What are you doing?

00:12:44.090 --> 00:12:45.120
Why are you like this?

00:12:45.120 --> 00:12:45.650
Cheer up.

00:12:45.670 --> 00:12:46.360
No, no.

00:12:46.390 --> 00:12:48.080
-It's the start of a new year—no tears.
-No, I just feel...

00:12:48.080 --> 00:12:49.130
Right? It's New Year's.

00:12:49.130 --> 00:12:49.920
I'm actually happy.

00:12:49.920 --> 00:12:51.080
Happy for Lan, right?

00:12:51.080 --> 00:12:51.920
Alright, Yi.

00:12:51.940 --> 00:12:52.480
Seriously.

00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:53.240
No. Yeah.

00:12:53.260 --> 00:12:54.180
My bad.

00:12:54.210 --> 00:12:55.200
Here, let me pour you another cup.

00:12:55.200 --> 00:12:58.110
Actually, our Xiaole is the lucky one.

00:12:58.200 --> 00:13:01.380
Right? I've watched Lan grow up,
and I really like her.

00:13:01.630 --> 00:13:02.630
Really, Yi, I'm telling you,

00:13:02.630 --> 00:13:04.830
in my heart, no one could compare to her.

00:13:07.390 --> 00:13:08.120
Come on, cheers!

00:13:08.120 --> 00:13:08.750
Well,

00:13:08.750 --> 00:13:10.000
thank you, thank you again.

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:11.870
Come on. Cheers.

00:13:11.870 --> 00:13:12.600
Xiaole!

00:13:13.480 --> 00:13:14.870
Did you cheat on my sister?

00:13:14.870 --> 00:13:16.590
I saw you kissing another woman—

00:13:16.590 --> 00:13:17.750
twice!

00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:18.600
Xuan,

00:13:19.120 --> 00:13:20.360
what nonsense are you talking about?

00:13:20.360 --> 00:13:20.990
Shut it.

00:13:21.960 --> 00:13:24.120
What are you doing
bringing this up on New Year's?

00:13:24.120 --> 00:13:25.600
What are you talking about,
making things up?

00:13:25.600 --> 00:13:26.530
What's going on?

00:13:28.390 --> 00:13:29.230
Xiaole,

00:13:29.480 --> 00:13:29.970
you...

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:31.660
What's going on with all this?

00:13:35.600 --> 00:13:36.200
Uncle...

00:13:39.550 --> 00:13:40.810
We really did break up.

00:13:43.080 --> 00:13:44.080
You broke up?

00:13:45.240 --> 00:13:47.330
My sixth sense is incredible.

00:13:47.510 --> 00:13:49.800
Tong Xiaole, you little brat!

00:13:52.630 --> 00:13:53.750
You'd better
explain yourself to me clearly!

00:13:53.750 --> 00:13:54.480
Calm down!

00:13:54.480 --> 00:13:55.120
Explain yourself!

00:13:55.120 --> 00:13:56.390
It's all a misunderstanding!

00:13:56.390 --> 00:13:57.590
A misunderstanding?

00:13:58.360 --> 00:14:00.000
Xuan saw it with his own eyes!

00:14:00.360 --> 00:14:01.360
Explain to me clearly!

00:14:01.360 --> 00:14:02.240
What happened?

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:05.000
If you don't explain clearly,

00:14:05.000 --> 00:14:06.600
forget celebrating the New Year!

00:14:06.600 --> 00:14:08.000
Celebrate the New Year, my foot.

00:14:08.000 --> 00:14:09.510
What are you doing?

00:14:09.510 --> 00:14:11.790
What are you trying to do?

00:14:14.320 --> 00:14:15.840
My legs are bad enough as it is—

00:14:15.840 --> 00:14:17.240
are you trying to kill me?

00:14:20.000 --> 00:14:21.240
Sit down first. Sit.

00:14:22.120 --> 00:14:22.750
I'm sorry.

00:14:23.080 --> 00:14:24.880
I got a bit carried away just now.

00:14:25.240 --> 00:14:26.500
What's wrong with you?

00:14:26.630 --> 00:14:27.840
This has nothing to do with you.

00:14:27.840 --> 00:14:29.080
You alright, right?

00:14:33.960 --> 00:14:35.360
I just want to know...

00:14:36.600 --> 00:14:37.870
When did you break up?

00:14:39.080 --> 00:14:39.870
It was...

00:14:39.870 --> 00:14:41.370
Shut it! Let him speak!

00:14:46.200 --> 00:14:47.660
It was a year and a half ago.

00:14:52.120 --> 00:14:53.000
I remember now.

00:14:54.510 --> 00:14:57.080
Lan failed to graduate
because you broke up with her, right?

00:14:57.080 --> 00:14:57.930
No! No!

00:14:58.000 --> 00:14:59.480
You brat!

00:14:59.510 --> 00:15:01.630
What did Lan ever do wrong to you?

00:15:01.630 --> 00:15:03.240
How could you not want Lan anymore?

00:15:03.240 --> 00:15:07.000
We haven't even asked everything—
why are you so worked up?

00:15:07.020 --> 00:15:08.140
Calm down!

00:15:08.170 --> 00:15:09.110
You ask!

00:15:09.200 --> 00:15:10.730
Who initiated the breakup?

00:15:11.320 --> 00:15:11.980
I did.

00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:12.960
See?

00:15:13.390 --> 00:15:14.720
He initiated it, right?

00:15:14.840 --> 00:15:15.870
You brat...

00:15:15.870 --> 00:15:16.480
Dad!

00:15:16.960 --> 00:15:17.910
I initiated it.

00:15:20.240 --> 00:15:20.750
You...

00:15:22.120 --> 00:15:22.520
You...

00:15:23.870 --> 00:15:25.320
Y-You initiated the breakup?

00:15:25.320 --> 00:15:25.790
Yes.

00:15:25.870 --> 00:15:27.120
He must've forced you, right?

00:15:27.120 --> 00:15:27.750
No!

00:15:28.120 --> 00:15:30.050
I was the one who wanted to break up.

00:15:30.080 --> 00:15:32.480
The "other woman" my brother mentioned...

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:33.790
was me!

00:15:36.120 --> 00:15:36.870
Look at this!

00:15:37.630 --> 00:15:38.860
What is all this mess?

00:15:39.000 --> 00:15:41.530
Why do you always blame my son
for everything?

00:15:41.630 --> 00:15:42.720
I'll leave the past aside for now.

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:43.380
Look at you,

00:15:43.480 --> 00:15:44.870
you're blaming my son
for everything again!

00:15:44.870 --> 00:15:46.480
Let's talk nicely. Calm down.

00:15:46.480 --> 00:15:47.120
You...

00:15:47.120 --> 00:15:49.000
-Uncle Dong, sit down.
-Sit.

00:15:50.840 --> 00:15:53.360
I think these two kids
get along quite well now.

00:15:53.360 --> 00:15:54.020
Don't they?

00:15:54.480 --> 00:15:56.320
Why are you worrying so much for nothing?

00:15:56.320 --> 00:15:58.840
Besides, they haven't even told us
why they broke up.

00:15:58.840 --> 00:16:00.600
There must've been a reason, right, Lan?

00:16:00.600 --> 00:16:01.240
Fine.

00:16:04.040 --> 00:16:04.710
Lan.

00:16:06.120 --> 00:16:07.120
Dad is asking you,

00:16:07.480 --> 00:16:09.000
why on earth did you break up?

00:16:09.000 --> 00:16:10.370
Xiaole is a good kid.

00:16:10.600 --> 00:16:11.510
No reason.

00:16:12.080 --> 00:16:13.480
I just wanted to break up.

00:16:14.870 --> 00:16:16.000
Is there still a chance for you two?

00:16:16.000 --> 00:16:17.330
I'll state my position—

00:16:18.840 --> 00:16:19.900
I'll listen to Lan.

00:16:25.600 --> 00:16:26.000
Uncle.

00:16:27.120 --> 00:16:28.480
I'd like to...

00:16:29.080 --> 00:16:30.740
talk to Lan for a moment, may I?

00:16:31.360 --> 00:16:32.000
Go ahead.

00:16:32.720 --> 00:16:33.520
Come back soon

00:16:33.600 --> 00:16:34.810
for dumplings.

00:16:34.870 --> 00:16:35.910
Hurry up.

00:16:36.000 --> 00:16:36.600
Lan.

00:16:37.360 --> 00:16:37.870
Then...

00:16:40.390 --> 00:16:41.070
Let's go.

00:17:13.480 --> 00:17:13.930
Why...

00:17:14.109 --> 00:17:15.170
Why did you

00:17:15.240 --> 00:17:16.690
admit it just now?

00:17:16.920 --> 00:17:19.310
My dad knows now—he won't let this go.

00:17:20.349 --> 00:17:21.200
I...

00:17:21.829 --> 00:17:23.650
was just stating the facts.

00:17:24.160 --> 00:17:25.030
Or...

00:17:26.400 --> 00:17:27.640
did you want me to lie?

00:17:31.310 --> 00:17:32.090
Yi...

00:17:33.310 --> 00:17:34.100
I really...

00:17:34.360 --> 00:17:35.210
Okay, okay.

00:17:36.110 --> 00:17:37.590
Let me say something.

00:17:39.790 --> 00:17:40.750
Right now,

00:17:40.750 --> 00:17:41.680
it's not certain

00:17:42.070 --> 00:17:43.590
that these two kids have broken up yet.

00:17:43.590 --> 00:17:44.550
I think we shouldn't

00:17:44.550 --> 00:17:45.750
spread this around for now.

00:17:45.750 --> 00:17:48.110
It wouldn't look good
with all the neighbors watching.

00:17:48.110 --> 00:17:48.830
What?

00:17:49.960 --> 00:17:51.090
That's not right.

00:17:51.680 --> 00:17:52.790
Let me tell you, Yi,

00:17:53.110 --> 00:17:55.590
my son's suitors have practically
worn out my doorstep!

00:17:55.590 --> 00:17:56.220
Yes, yes.

00:17:56.680 --> 00:17:57.400
Seriously.

00:17:57.680 --> 00:17:58.790
We don't need to brag.

00:17:58.790 --> 00:17:59.790
I'm not bragging.

00:17:59.920 --> 00:18:02.110
Let the kids decide for themselves,

00:18:02.110 --> 00:18:02.750
right?

00:18:02.860 --> 00:18:03.890
Yes, absolutely.

00:18:04.030 --> 00:18:04.750
Hey,

00:18:05.200 --> 00:18:06.350
can you turn the page?

00:18:06.350 --> 00:18:07.200
I can't. I can't let go of all this.

00:18:07.200 --> 00:18:08.310
I'll chug one for you.

00:18:08.310 --> 00:18:09.590
Bottoms up! Bottoms up! Okay?

00:18:09.590 --> 00:18:10.350
Stop it.

00:18:10.350 --> 00:18:11.200
I'll drink it! Bottoms up!

00:18:11.200 --> 00:18:11.790
Don't be mad anymore.

00:18:11.790 --> 00:18:13.350
Look at you just now!

00:18:13.350 --> 00:18:14.680
Did you think I couldn't take you?

00:18:14.680 --> 00:18:15.640
Tong, keep your voice down.

00:18:15.640 --> 00:18:16.880
The kids might hear.

00:18:16.880 --> 00:18:18.110
I can't see anything.

00:18:18.880 --> 00:18:20.930
My dad must still be furious.

00:18:21.390 --> 00:18:22.720
Yeah, can't see a thing.

00:18:36.350 --> 00:18:36.660
I'll head home later by myself.

00:18:36.660 --> 00:18:39.520
♪ Dusk gently fell on the coastline ♪

00:18:40.250 --> 00:18:43.220
♪ The quietly passing breeze
gave the clouds a kiss ♪

00:18:43.690 --> 00:18:45.360
♪ The Earth keeps spinning round ♪

00:18:45.380 --> 00:18:47.100
♪ Painted with shades of romance ♪

00:18:47.600 --> 00:18:48.880
♪ That was the moment I met you ♪

00:18:48.880 --> 00:18:49.940
Then why did you...

00:18:50.540 --> 00:18:50.570
kiss me in the park just now?

00:18:50.570 --> 00:18:53.330
♪ Even mountains and seas
can't separate us ♪

00:18:54.090 --> 00:18:57.080
♪ I wish I could turn into a bird
to explore the world for you ♪

00:18:57.620 --> 00:18:57.640
♪ The vast, boundless Milky Way ♪

00:18:57.640 --> 00:18:58.700
Because I like you.

00:18:59.190 --> 00:19:00.400
♪ Sings its tender serenade ♪

00:19:00.400 --> 00:19:01.030
Then...

00:19:01.150 --> 00:19:02.920
♪ I can't live a second without you ♪

00:19:02.920 --> 00:19:04.420
what are we now?

00:19:04.530 --> 00:19:07.750
♪ Looking forward
to the next beautiful dream ♪

00:19:08.050 --> 00:19:09.420
♪ I just want to be with you ♪

00:19:09.610 --> 00:19:12.560
♪ To see the most romantic starry sky
together ♪

00:19:12.880 --> 00:19:16.200
♪ The evening breeze tells
heartfelt emotions ♪

00:19:16.200 --> 00:19:17.730
This kind of relationship.

00:19:17.790 --> 00:19:19.500
♪ All the stars surround you ♪

00:19:19.530 --> 00:19:20.160
♪ The moon smiles at you ♪

00:19:20.160 --> 00:19:21.230
What kind of relationship

00:19:21.230 --> 00:19:21.920
♪ I give you all the good things
in the world ♪

00:19:21.920 --> 00:19:23.720
is "this kind of relationship"?

00:19:24.690 --> 00:19:26.450
♪ And the light in your eyes ♪

00:19:26.480 --> 00:19:28.530
♪ Shines like diamonds ♪

00:19:28.850 --> 00:19:31.650
♪ Drawing an exclamation mark
in my world ♪

00:19:31.730 --> 00:19:33.200
♪ The evening breeze embraces you ♪

00:19:33.230 --> 00:19:33.920
♪ And I run towards you ♪

00:19:33.920 --> 00:19:34.550
Fine.

00:19:35.030 --> 00:19:38.350
♪ I hear our passionate heartbeats ♪

00:19:38.580 --> 00:19:40.060
♪ We borrow a dream ♪

00:19:40.080 --> 00:19:40.510
♪ To build a castle ♪

00:19:40.510 --> 00:19:41.710
You're my boyfriend.

00:19:42.520 --> 00:19:44.860
♪ Every star is a romantic symbol ♪

00:19:44.930 --> 00:19:47.430
♪ Let me find you ♪

00:19:49.060 --> 00:19:50.700
♪ All the stars surround you ♪

00:19:50.720 --> 00:19:52.450
♪ The moon smiles at you ♪

00:19:52.480 --> 00:19:55.660
♪ I give you all the good things
in the world ♪

00:19:56.090 --> 00:19:57.270
♪ And the light in your eyes ♪

00:19:57.270 --> 00:19:57.720
Why are you taking photos of them?

00:19:57.720 --> 00:19:58.310
♪ Shines like diamonds ♪

00:19:58.310 --> 00:19:59.270
Well, they made up.

00:19:59.270 --> 00:20:00.050
I have to record it.

00:20:00.050 --> 00:20:00.830
♪ Drawing an exclamation mark
in my world ♪

00:20:00.830 --> 00:20:02.880
So the neighbors don't misunderstand.

00:20:02.880 --> 00:20:04.310
♪ The evening breeze embraces you ♪

00:20:04.330 --> 00:20:06.210
♪ And I run towards you ♪

00:20:06.290 --> 00:20:09.530
♪ I hear our passionate heartbeats ♪

00:20:09.830 --> 00:20:11.150
♪ We borrow a dream ♪

00:20:11.250 --> 00:20:13.470
♪ To build a castle ♪

00:20:13.780 --> 00:20:16.070
♪ Every star is a romantic symbol ♪

00:20:16.130 --> 00:20:18.640
♪ Let me find you ♪

00:20:19.880 --> 00:20:21.140
You're my girlfriend?

00:20:35.880 --> 00:20:36.750
My girlfriend!

00:20:38.010 --> 00:20:40.200
When are you planning to go abroad again?

00:20:40.200 --> 00:20:41.330
I'd like to apply...

00:20:41.590 --> 00:20:42.390
to go with you.

00:20:43.640 --> 00:20:44.400
Okay.

00:20:45.110 --> 00:20:48.370
I'm thinking of traveling around
a few other cities first,

00:20:48.400 --> 00:20:51.240
then coming back for my final performance.

00:20:51.750 --> 00:20:54.420
Well... if you're going to other cities,

00:20:54.510 --> 00:20:55.830
I want to go with you

00:20:56.030 --> 00:20:57.600
and then wait with you

00:20:57.630 --> 00:20:59.160
for the final performance.

00:20:59.780 --> 00:21:00.580
Okay.

00:21:03.130 --> 00:21:06.030
Can you take me with you
when you take photos in the future?

00:21:06.030 --> 00:21:07.000
Of course I can.

00:21:07.640 --> 00:21:08.790
Then, from now on,

00:21:08.980 --> 00:21:09.910
wherever you go,

00:21:10.050 --> 00:21:10.730
I go.

00:21:11.160 --> 00:21:11.960
Wherever I go,

00:21:12.390 --> 00:21:13.120
you go.

00:21:18.930 --> 00:21:21.330
Wherever you go, I go.
Wherever I go, you go.

00:21:22.400 --> 00:21:23.350
Pinky swear,

00:21:24.160 --> 00:21:25.120
cross my heart—

00:21:25.570 --> 00:21:26.380
no

00:21:27.180 --> 00:21:28.100
take-backs.

00:21:36.310 --> 00:21:38.440
I don't want to be apart from you again!

00:21:39.470 --> 00:21:41.000
As long as you don't dump me,

00:21:41.040 --> 00:21:42.200
we'll never be apart.

00:21:42.200 --> 00:21:44.270
Why are you bringing that up again?

00:21:54.110 --> 00:21:54.710
Yi Lan,

00:21:55.110 --> 00:21:58.240
Xiaole has prepared
a spectacular performance for you.

00:22:21.270 --> 00:22:22.550
You're all here.

00:22:29.590 --> 00:22:30.900
Why are you here, too?

00:22:31.350 --> 00:22:32.680
I'm the organizer.

00:22:33.000 --> 00:22:35.120
It'd be weird if I didn't show up.

00:22:40.830 --> 00:22:42.640
Wasn't it supposed to be a performance?

00:22:42.640 --> 00:22:43.390
It is.

00:22:43.920 --> 00:22:44.920
Our performance.

00:22:55.550 --> 00:22:56.280
I'm sorry—

00:22:57.400 --> 00:22:58.750
I invited everyone here

00:22:59.030 --> 00:23:00.830
without telling you in advance.

00:23:07.870 --> 00:23:09.780
Looking at

00:23:10.270 --> 00:23:13.110
how things are set up today,
you should be able to guess

00:23:13.110 --> 00:23:15.370
that I have something to tell you, right?

00:23:16.110 --> 00:23:16.990
Then go ahead.

00:23:17.160 --> 00:23:18.400
I'm listening.

00:23:21.070 --> 00:23:21.640
Yi Lan!

00:23:23.350 --> 00:23:24.480
I'm really grateful

00:23:24.960 --> 00:23:26.820
that you're willing to be with me.

00:23:27.750 --> 00:23:28.720
You are like

00:23:29.920 --> 00:23:32.730
sunshine on a cold winter day,

00:23:33.640 --> 00:23:35.240
lighting up my whole world.

00:23:38.440 --> 00:23:39.900
You are like the Monkey King
wielding the Golden Cudgel...

00:23:39.900 --> 00:23:42.700
♪ That crumpled prayer flag ♪

00:23:42.910 --> 00:23:44.590
♪ Has been hanging there for years ♪

00:23:44.590 --> 00:23:46.020
sweeping away all the darkness and gloom
in my life.

00:23:46.020 --> 00:23:49.050
♪ Stacks of sturdy photos ♪

00:23:49.140 --> 00:23:50.260
♪ Notes scribbled on their backs ♪

00:23:50.260 --> 00:23:51.660
As long as you're with me,

00:23:52.350 --> 00:23:53.440
even facing

00:23:53.830 --> 00:23:55.480
♪ With edges all askew ♪

00:23:55.480 --> 00:23:58.000
ten thousand heavenly soldiers
and the eighty-one ordeals,

00:23:58.000 --> 00:23:58.620
♪ A metaphor for understanding ♪

00:23:58.620 --> 00:24:00.820
I'll keep moving forward, unwavering.

00:24:03.630 --> 00:24:04.500
You once asked me

00:24:04.500 --> 00:24:05.590
♪ In dreams ♪

00:24:05.590 --> 00:24:07.590
what the difference was
between friendship and love.

00:24:07.590 --> 00:24:10.020
♪ We meet silently ♪

00:24:10.020 --> 00:24:10.730
I've thought about it
for a long, long time.

00:24:10.730 --> 00:24:13.240
♪ Bit by bit, I move forward ♪

00:24:13.780 --> 00:24:15.110
♪ She smiles just as she used to ♪

00:24:15.110 --> 00:24:17.160
Back when we were friends,

00:24:17.880 --> 00:24:18.320
when you were upset,

00:24:18.320 --> 00:24:20.000
♪ I shouldn't have ♪

00:24:20.000 --> 00:24:21.270
I'd feel sad, too.

00:24:22.590 --> 00:24:24.960
When you were happy,
♪ Turned us into two halves
of a shattered heart ♪

00:24:24.960 --> 00:24:26.200
I'd be happy, too.

00:24:27.140 --> 00:24:29.200
♪ Secrets sink deep ♪

00:24:29.200 --> 00:24:30.240
But now,

00:24:30.360 --> 00:24:31.920
♪ Clouds surge and roll like ocean waves ♪

00:24:31.920 --> 00:24:33.240
even when I'm unhappy,

00:24:33.260 --> 00:24:34.160
♪ What awaits us is not sunlight ♪

00:24:34.160 --> 00:24:35.820
I still want to make you happy.

00:24:38.790 --> 00:24:39.400
So I've decided...

00:24:39.400 --> 00:24:42.210
♪ When I turn around ♪

00:24:42.620 --> 00:24:42.830
♪ The story begins ♪

00:24:42.830 --> 00:24:45.680
to spend my whole life
answering that question.

00:24:45.680 --> 00:24:47.920
♪ Without a trace ♪

00:24:49.480 --> 00:24:50.440
Will you...

00:24:51.240 --> 00:24:51.620
have me?

00:24:51.620 --> 00:24:54.050
♪ Later I became a bird, searching ♪

00:24:54.050 --> 00:24:55.630
Will you have me?

00:24:57.980 --> 00:25:00.100
♪ Flying forward all alone ♪

00:25:00.190 --> 00:25:00.850
♪ Self-comfort is inevitable ♪

00:25:00.850 --> 00:25:02.410
I do!

00:25:04.180 --> 00:25:06.380
♪ Forgive me for not giving up yet ♪

00:25:07.600 --> 00:25:09.030
♪ I won't give up ♪

00:25:09.030 --> 00:25:09.920
Then...

00:25:10.260 --> 00:25:15.870
♪ Choosing an answer,
repeating the ending a few times ♪

00:25:16.540 --> 00:25:17.150
♪ I fly in the crowd
with my nest branches ♪

00:25:17.150 --> 00:25:18.990
I'm willing to be yours!

00:25:22.660 --> 00:25:24.080
♪ Watching them ♪

00:25:24.190 --> 00:25:26.350
♪ Come and go as the seasons change ♪

00:25:26.350 --> 00:25:28.110
I'm willing to have you!

00:25:28.810 --> 00:25:32.110
♪ But I still can't do it ♪

00:25:32.170 --> 00:25:34.230
♪ I can't ♪

00:25:34.820 --> 00:25:41.540
♪ Follow in the footsteps of the monsoon ♪

00:25:48.990 --> 00:25:50.120
I have something

00:25:50.510 --> 00:25:51.650
to say to you as well.

00:25:51.910 --> 00:25:54.040
She says she has something to say to me!

00:25:59.650 --> 00:26:00.410
Xiaole.

00:26:02.040 --> 00:26:03.660
Thank you for always

00:26:04.150 --> 00:26:05.630
seeing me as the best,

00:26:05.780 --> 00:26:07.440
the finest version of myself.

00:26:07.450 --> 00:26:08.280
Thank you

00:26:08.790 --> 00:26:10.850
for always understanding me so well.

00:26:12.360 --> 00:26:15.230
Thank you for always choosing me
with such certainty

00:26:15.230 --> 00:26:16.230
and for loving me.

00:26:17.230 --> 00:26:18.780
Your presence makes me feel

00:26:19.580 --> 00:26:20.900
so strong.

00:26:22.670 --> 00:26:23.990
I want to ride

00:26:24.240 --> 00:26:24.640
♪ She left in spring ♪

00:26:24.640 --> 00:26:27.140
the seven-colored clouds with you

00:26:27.400 --> 00:26:27.800
and take on the whole world together!

00:26:27.800 --> 00:26:30.610
♪ Gone with her was cherry blossoms ♪

00:26:30.850 --> 00:26:31.190
I want to be with you forever and ever!

00:26:31.190 --> 00:26:32.940
♪ On the once youthful face ♪

00:26:32.940 --> 00:26:33.980
Kiss!

00:26:34.010 --> 00:26:34.930
Kiss!

00:26:34.950 --> 00:26:35.000
Kiss!

00:26:35.000 --> 00:26:36.060
♪ There were tears amidst confusion ♪

00:26:36.060 --> 00:26:37.270
Kiss!

00:26:37.290 --> 00:26:38.370
-Kiss! Kiss!
-Kiss!

00:26:38.370 --> 00:26:38.990
♪ She left in spring ♪

00:26:38.990 --> 00:26:39.790
Kiss!

00:26:42.000 --> 00:26:42.240
♪ All was like a dream ♪

00:26:42.240 --> 00:26:42.970
Should we...

00:26:43.100 --> 00:26:44.230
do as they say?

00:26:44.300 --> 00:26:45.280
Then let's do it.

00:26:45.280 --> 00:26:47.900
♪ Youth never lasts ♪

00:26:49.290 --> 00:26:51.770
♪ Just let her go ♪

00:26:53.000 --> 00:26:55.200
♪ The paper plane that was once set free ♪

00:26:55.370 --> 00:26:58.710
♪ Will find its way back
to the old desk and chair at school ♪

00:26:59.070 --> 00:27:02.150
♪ All stories have yet to end ♪

00:27:02.480 --> 00:27:03.850
♪ Let me write for you ♪

00:27:03.960 --> 00:27:07.760
♪ An old CD will witness
our ever-ending dreams ♪

00:27:07.870 --> 00:27:10.650
♪ Youth is nothing but a farce ♪

00:27:10.950 --> 00:27:13.900
♪ In which everyone has fun till the end ♪

00:27:14.200 --> 00:27:17.670
♪ It's a pity time always sneaks away ♪

00:27:17.890 --> 00:27:20.270
♪ Leaving behind so many headaches ♪

00:27:20.360 --> 00:27:21.750
♪ We never had the time to look back on ♪

00:27:21.990 --> 00:27:24.800
♪ Youth is nothing but a farce ♪

00:27:25.050 --> 00:27:27.440
♪ We live it wholeheartedly ♪

00:27:27.440 --> 00:27:28.230
[We sincerely invite you and your family
to witness our moment of happiness.]

00:27:28.230 --> 00:27:29.920
♪ Joy and sorrow are woven together ♪

00:27:29.920 --> 00:27:32.190
[Hey, it's been a while.
See you at the wedding!]

00:27:32.190 --> 00:27:35.660
♪ Every experience will bring me closer ♪

00:27:35.890 --> 00:27:36.760
♪ To myself ♪